<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Employment Agreement</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.6; color: #000; padding: 60px 80px; background: white; }
        .header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 30px; border-bottom: 3px solid #000; padding-bottom: 20px; }
        .document-title { font-size: 24pt; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 15px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .date { text-align: right; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 20px; color: #555; }
        .info-box { background: #f8f8f8; border: 2px solid #333; padding: 25px; margin: 30px 0; border-radius: 5px; }
        .info-box h3 { margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; text-transform: uppercase; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd; padding-bottom: 5px; }
        .info-row { display: flex; margin-bottom: 8px; }
        .info-label { font-weight: bold; width: 200px; flex-shrink: 0; }
        .info-value { flex: 1; }
        .section { margin: 25px 0; }
        .section-title { font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .section-content { text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        ul { margin-left: 40px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        li { margin-bottom: 5px; }
        strong { font-weight: bold; }
        .form-row { margin-top: 30px; page-break-inside: avoid; }
        .form-label { font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .form-line { border-bottom: 1px solid #000; min-height: 40px; margin-bottom: 15px; }
        .signature-section { margin-top: 40px; page-break-inside: avoid; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header"><div class="document-title">EMPLOYMENT AGREEMENT</div></div>
    <div class="date">Effective Date: {{date}}</div>
    <div class="info-box">
        <h3>Employer Information</h3>
        <div class="info-row"><div class="info-label">Employer:</div><div class="info-value">{{BusinessName}}</div></div>
        <div class="info-row"><div class="info-label">Legal Entity:</div><div class="info-value">{{LegalEntityName}}</div></div>
        <div class="info-row"><div class="info-label">Address:</div><div class="info-value">{{BusinessAddress}}</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-content">
            This Employment Agreement ("Agreement") is between <strong>{{BusinessName}}</strong> ("Employer") and the individual signing below ("Employee").
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">1. POSITION AND DUTIES</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Employee is hired for the position of [Job Title] and will perform duties including but not limited to: [specific responsibilities]. Employee will report to [supervisor/manager] and work at {{BusinessAddress}}.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">2. EMPLOYMENT TYPE</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            This is an [at-will, full-time, part-time] position. Employment is at-will, meaning either party may terminate the relationship at any time with or without cause or notice, subject to applicable law.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">3. COMPENSATION</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Employee will be paid [hourly rate/annual salary] as outlined in the offer letter. Compensation is paid [weekly, bi-weekly, monthly] via [direct deposit, check]. Employee is [exempt/non-exempt] from overtime under the Fair Labor Standards Act.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">4. BENEFITS</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Employee is eligible for benefits as outlined in the Employee Handbook, which may include: health insurance, paid time off, retirement plans, and other benefits. Benefit eligibility and terms are subject to plan documents.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">5. WORK SCHEDULE</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Employee's standard work schedule is [days and hours]. Employer may require additional hours or schedule changes as business needs dictate.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">6. CONFIDENTIALITY AND NON-DISCLOSURE</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Employee agrees to maintain confidentiality of all proprietary information, including client lists, business strategies, financial information, and trade secrets. This obligation continues after employment ends.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">7. INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            All work product, inventions, or intellectual property created by Employee during employment belongs to Employer.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">8. TERMINATION</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            Either party may terminate this Agreement at any time. Upon termination, Employee must return all company property and will receive final compensation as required by law.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section">
        <div class="section-title">9. GOVERNING LAW</div>
        <div class="section-content">
            This Agreement is governed by the laws of <strong>{{Jurisdiction}}</strong> and complies with federal and state employment laws.
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="signature-section">
        <div class="form-row"><div class="form-label">Employer:</div><div class="form-line">{{BusinessName}}</div></div>
        <div class="form-row"><div class="form-label">Authorized Signature:</div><div class="form-line"></div></div>
        <div class="form-row"><div class="form-label">Date:</div><div class="form-line"></div></div>
        <div class="form-row" style="margin-top: 50px;"><div class="form-label">Employee Name:</div><div class="form-line"></div></div>
        <div class="form-row"><div class="form-label">Employee Signature:</div><div class="form-line"></div></div>
        <div class="form-row"><div class="form-label">Date:</div><div class="form-line"></div></div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>